OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith the odd light shower across the
OL,7,Feast, otherwise dry. This afternoon
OL,8,Fwill be dry with variable amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud, some brightness breaking
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,13,FThen cloud and rain will spread
OL,14,Fsoutheast across all parts overnight
OL,15,Ffollowed by clearer weather and a few
OL,16,Fshowers in the west.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,19,Fshowers, these turning more widespread
OL,20,Fand occasionally heavy during the
OL,21,Fafternoon. Colder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
