OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry for
OL,6,Fmost of Friday before rain spreads
OL,7,Fnortheast by evening. Mainly dry and
OL,8,Fbright Saturday. Breezy with showers
OL,9,Fon Sunday.
